content.html: Likes and retweets are signals for quality/well liked/popular tweets (quote tweets are more ambiguous and can be good or bad). View count is useless and only shows how dead the platform really is. Gives advertisers leverage to spend less, or reason to spend none.
content.value:
Likes and retweets are signals for quality/well liked/popular tweets (quote tweets are more ambiguous and can be good or bad).

View count is useless and only shows how dead the platform really is. Gives advertisers leverage to spend less, or reason to spend none.
